==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outreach
<hw>Out*reach"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To reach
beyond.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>outreach</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: outreach
<hw>outreach</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of reaching
out; an effort to build connections from one person or group to another;
<as>as, the Police Department instituted a community <ex>outreach</ex>
program</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The extension of assistance or services to persons
or groups not previously served.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outreason</ent>⟦br⟧
